snippet.title: Hands of Necromancy II - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Hands of Necromancy II is coming on September 16, 2024!
A dark fantasy FPS sequel, inspired by classics such as Heretic and Doom. Choose from two characters, wield new weapons and learn even more powerful spells and transformations to prove once and for all that you are the supreme Necromancer, master of death itself!

Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2706450/Hands_of_Necromancy_II/

Follow us: https://linktr.ee/fulqrumpublishing
